<br>
The only thing that doesnt make sense to me, from a content point of view, is that this new Temple of Cazic Thule zone is arguably more difficult than the Plane of Fear.. home of the god Cazic Thule. How does a temple that worships a god become more powerful than the god himself? (I know mobs arent as tough as Cazic himself, but the zone itself is harder in my opinion).<br>
<br>
Frankly, if your crying about Verant taking away a mid level zone I would say to you you need to go out and explore more. There are plenty of midrange dungeons now, about 3 times as many mid range zones now as there where when EQ was released.<br>
<br>
Rex is also correct about the average level of player rising and  it is far easier to level in EQ today then it was 3 years ago so verant is really just adjusting accordingly to accomodate the player base.<br>
